rComments: Feels like she treated the class as more of a side job or hobby, and that is never okay. The class is only 2 credits, but it gives you enough work to feel like a 3-4 cred hour course. Very awkward feel, and she confuses everyone with what's expected. The class is also a very small class. 12 people registered, 8 only showed up & 4 dropped. NoGo...
